
PRIVACY POLICY
Last updated March 05, 2024

This privacy notice for _______("we," "us," or "our"), describes how and why we might collect, store, use and/or share ("process") your information when you use our services ("Services"), such as when you:

    - Download and use our mobile application (Digital dalali), or any other application of ours that links to this privacy notice
    - Engage with us in other related ways, including any sales, marketing, or events

Questions or concerns? Reading this privacy notice will help you understand your privacy rights and choices. If you do not agree with our policies and practices, please do not use our Services. If you still have any questions or concerns, please contact us at gluckiam@gmail.com.
SUMMARY OF KEY POINTS

What personal information do we process?
We process your personal information when you use our Services. This can include information you provide to us, information generated during your use of our Services, and information we obtain from third parties.

What sensitive personal information do we process?
In limited cases, we process sensitive personal information about you, but only where you provide that information to us or give us permission to obtain it.

Do we share your personal information with third parties?
We share your personal information with third parties in certain circumstances, such as when we use third party service providers.

What security measures do we have in place?
We use appropriate security measures to protect the security of your personal information, both online and offline.

What rights and choices do you have?
You have certain rights in relation to your personal information, including the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information.

How can you exercise your rights and choices?
You can exercise your rights and choices by contacting us through the contact details provided in this privacy notice.
